Since you're going with Brave, here are two quick things you'll probably want to check right after installation:

Brave Rewards: It’s turned on by default. If you aren't interested in the BAT crypto system or seeing "sponsored" background images on your new tab page, you can toggle it off in brave://settings/rewards.

Widevine: If you plan on watching Netflix, Spotify, or Disney+, Brave will usually show a small pop-up asking for permission to install "Widevine." You’ll need to say yes to that, or DRM-protected video won't play.

